text: "Gypsy" is a 1982 song by British American band Fleetwood Mac. It was taken from their 13th studio album Fleetwood Mac. It went to number 12 in the United States, number 16 in Canada, number 17 in Australia, number 25 in Ireland, number 35 in Germany, number 42 in the Netherlands and number 46 in the United Kingdom. It did not chart in New Zealand. Category:1982 songs Category:1980s ballads Category:Rock ballads Category:Dream pop songs Category:Fleetwood Mac songs
